<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Turtle Shelter Project</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      color: #333;
    }

    header {
  background: #2e8b57;
  color: #fff;
  padding: 15px 0;
  position: sticky;
  top: 0;
  z-index: 1000;
  display: flex; /* Enables flexible layout */
  align-items: center; /* Centers content vertically */
}

header img {
  height: 50px; /* Adjust as needed */
  margin-left: 15px; /* Adds some spacing from the edge */
}

header nav {
  flex-grow: 1; /* Makes the nav section expand to fill available space */
  text-align: center; /* Centers the content horizontally */
}

header nav a {
  color: #fff;
  margin: 0 15px;
  text-decoration: none;
  font-size: 1.1em;
  font-weight: bold;
  transition: color 0.3s ease;
}

header nav a:hover {
  color: #c3e6cb;
}

    

    h2 {
      color: #2e8b57;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    h1 {
      color: #ffffff;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    

    p {
      font-size: 1.2em;
      line-height: 1.6;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .hero {
      background: #fff;
      color: rgb(255, 255, 255);
      text-align: center;
      padding: 100px 20px;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 2.8em;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .hero p {
      font-size: 1.3em;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .hero a {
      background: #fff;
      color: #2e8b57;
      padding: 15px 30px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-size: 1.2em;
      font-weight: bold;
      transition: background 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .hero a:hover {
      background: #2e8b57;
      color: #fff;
    }

    .hero {
  position: relative; /* Allows for an overlay */
  background: url('images/Picture11.jpg') no-repeat center center / cover;
  height: 50vh; /* Example height: full viewport height */
  color: #fff; /* Ensures text is readable on dark background */
  display: flex; /* Centers content inside the section */
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
  text-align: center;
}

.hero::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5); /* Dark haze effect */
  z-index: 1; /* Ensures the overlay is behind content */
}

.hero-content {
  position: relative; /* Keeps it above the overlay */
  z-index: 2; /* Ensures content appears on top of the overlay */
}

.hero h1,
.hero p {
  z-index: 2; /* Ensures text stays on top of the haze */
  color: #ffffff !important; /* Forces text to be white */
}



    ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
    }

    ul li {
      font-size: 1.2em;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    ul li a {
      color: #2e8b57;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: color 0.3s ease;
    }

    ul li a:hover {
      color: #1d6d45;
    }

    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      background: #2e8b57;
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 1em;
    }

    footer a {
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
      transition: color 0.3s ease;
    }

    footer a:hover {
      color: #c3e6cb;
    }

    

  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- Top Navigation Bar -->
  <header>
    <nav>
      <a href="/jens_story">Jen's Story</a>
      <a href="/sponsors">Sponsors</a>
      <a href="/about">About</a>
      <a href="/schedule_event">Schedule an Event</a>
      <a href="/volunteer">Volunteer</a>
      <a href="/login">Login</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  
  <section class="hero" style="background-color: #fff; color: #ffffff; text-align: center; padding: 100px 20px;">
    <div class="hero-content">
    <h1 style="font-size: 2.8em; margin-bottom: 20px;">Helping to Save The Lives of People Experiencing Homelessness</h1>
    <p style="font-size: 1.3em; margin-bottom: 30px;">Providing Insulated Vests as Portable Shelters to Those in Need.</p>
    <a href="https://turtleshelterproject.org/donate" style="background: #2e8b57; color: #fff; padding: 15px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-size: 1.2em; font-weight: bold; transition: background 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;">Donate Now</a>
    <h1>Database Configuration</h1>
    <table border="1">
      <tr>
        <th>Key</th>
        <th>Value</th>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Hostname</td>
        <td><%= dbConfig.hostname %></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Username</td>
        <td><%= dbConfig.username %></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Password</td>
        <td><%= dbConfig.password %></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Database Name</td>
        <td><%= dbConfig.dbName %></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Port</td>
        <td><%= dbConfig.port %></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>SSL</td>
        <td><%= dbConfig.ssl %></td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </div>
  </section>
  

  <!-- What is a Turtle Shelter Vest Section -->
  <section style="background-color: #fff; padding: 2rem; max-width: 800px; margin: 20px auto; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">
    <h2 style="color: #2e8b57; text-align: left;">What is a Turtle Shelter?</h2>
    <div style="text-align: left;">
      <img src="images/Original+logo+low+resolution.png" alt="Description of the image" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;">
  </div>  
    <p style="text-align: left; font-size: 1.2em; line-height: 1.6;">A high-tech but simple solution to help save lives - </p>
    <p style="text-align: left; font-size: 1.2em; line-height: 1.6;">It's a portable "shelter" you can carry with you, just like a turtle...</p>
    <p style="text-align: left; font-size: 1.2em; line-height: 1.6;">One winter when Jen was homeless, <B>7</B> of her friends froze to death.</p>
    <p style="text-align: left; font-size: 1.2em; line-height: 1.6;">Jen is no longer homeless and has figured out a solution:</p>
    <p style="text-align: left; font-size: 1.2em; line-height: 1.6;">High-tech foam vests that are inexpensive, keep a person warm up to 10 degrees below zero, and help <B>SAVE</B> lives.</p>
    <p style="text-align: left; font-size: 1.2em; line-height: 1.6;"><B>YOU</B> can request vests for your community - and you can make vests and have your friends, business colleagues, church members, or club make vests too!</p>
</section>


